Name: League Of Enthusiastic Losers
About the game: Vitya and Volodya are two best friends who are faced with all sorts of problems, the main one of which is eviction from the apartment for non-payment. Friends do not have enough money and they decide to look for treasure, in parallel doing their daily activities. Many adventures and new unexpected meetings await them. League of Enthusiastic Losers is an adventure game about caring for yourself and your friends, and about not having to be unhappy, just because you are a loser in the eyes of others. The game takes place in Moscow.
